        <img
          width="1000"
          height="1000"
          src="/assets/ProfilePicture.jpeg"
          alt="me"
        />
      </Hero>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Presentation</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Full stack developer based in Grenoble, passionate about web
            technologies, clean code, and constant improvement. Curious,
            rigorous, and motivated, I strive to understand things deeply and
            level up with each step.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            After a few years in the climbing world, I decided to retrain in web
            development — not a career switch, but the pursuit of a field I’ve
            always been drawn to: building, thinking, solving real-world
            problems.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Today, I work at Thomyris on a full-scale mail management system
            with anti-spam and antivirus filtering. A demanding backend
            (multi-tenant, filters, CI/CD), a clean front (Vue, Nuxt) — the
            perfect playground to learn and structure my skills.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            At the same time, I keep strengthening my foundations: Python,
            algorithms, software design, dev best practices. I progress line by
            line, through documentation, practice, and personal projects.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            I move forward with discipline, consistency, and passion — always
            seeking understanding, clarity, and purpose in the code I write.
          </p>
        </div>
